OL,3,CMan who stalked Strictly star for
OL,4,Cyears avoids being sent to jail
OL,6,FA Wirral man who stalked Strictly Come
OL,7,FDancing judge Shirley Ballas over a
OL,8,Fsix year period has avoided being sent
OL,9,Fto prison at Liverpool Crown Court.
OL,11,FKyle Shaw, 37, has been handed a 20-
OL,12,Fmonth prison sentence, suspended for
OL,13,F20 months after he admitted in
OL,14,FFebruary to stalking Ballas, 64,
OL,15,Fcausing serious harm or distress,
OL,16,Fbetween August 31 2017 and November 29
OL,17,F2023.
