OL,3,CMan who stalked Strictly star for
OL,4,Cyears avoids being sent to jail
OL,6,FShaw, from Birkenhead, embarked on a
OL,7,F"persistent campaign of contact"
OL,8,Fsending messages and threats to the
OL,9,Fdancer and her friends and colleagues
OL,10,Fbecause he believed her late brother,
OL,11,FDavid Rich, was his father, Liverpool
OL,12,FCrown Court heard.
OL,14,FA judge at an earlier hearing had
OL,15,Fwarned Shaw he faced the possibility
OL,16,Fof an immediate custodial sentence
OL,17,Fafter he also admitted possession of
OL,18,Fcannabis.
