OL,3,CMan who stalked Strictly star for
OL,4,Cyears avoids being sent to jail
OL,6,FNicola Daley, prosecuting, said: "He
OL,7,Fbelieved, and it's evident from what
OL,8,Fhe was told by his mother, that her
OL,9,Flate brother was his father."
OL,11,FThe court heard there was no evidence
OL,12,Fthat his belief was incorrect, but
OL,13,Fthere was "limited evidence" it was
OL,14,Fcorrect.
OL,16,FMs Daley said in messages Shaw accused
OL,17,FBallas of being responsible for the
OL,18,Fdeath of her brother, who took his own
OL,19,Flife in 2003 at the age of 44. He also
OL,20,Fset up social media accounts in her
OL,21,Fbrother's name.
