OL,3,CMan who stalked Strictly star for
OL,4,Cyears avoids being sent to jail
OL,6,FHe approached Ballas's mother, 86-year-
OL,7,Fold Audrey Rich, when shopping in
OL,8,FWirral in 2019, the court heard,
OL,9,Fleading Ballas to move her mother from
OL,10,FMerseyside to London.
OL,12,FThe court heard he told Ms Rich she
OL,13,Fwas his grandmother and continued to
OL,14,Ffollow her around the shop when she
OL,15,Fdid not want to speak to him.
OL,17,FMs Daley said Ballas became reluctant
OL,18,Fto socialise with colleagues and
OL,19,Fstopped using public transport.
