OL,3,CMan who stalked Strictly star for
OL,4,Cyears avoids being sent to jail
OL,6,FShe said: "She described having
OL,7,Fsleepless nights worrying about
OL,8,Fherself and her family's safety and
OL,9,Fbeing particularly distressed when
OL,10,Fsuggestions were made to her that she
OL,11,Fand her mother were responsible for
OL,12,Fher brother taking his own life."
OL,14,FShaw also sent messages to her niece
OL,15,FMary Assall, former partner Daniel
OL,16,FTaylor and to work colleagues from
OL,17,FLoose Women and Strictly Come Dancing.
