OL,3,CMan who stalked Strictly star for
OL,4,Cyears avoids being sent to jail
OL,6,FThe court heard when Ballas had book
OL,7,Fsignings planned in Wirral Shaw
OL,8,Fmessaged her saying: "I can't wait to
OL,9,Fmeet you for the first time Aunty
OL,10,FShirley. Hopefully I can get an
OL,11,Fautograph."
OL,13,FJohn Weate, defending, said Shaw had
OL,14,Fsuffered complex mental health issues
OL,15,Fsince childhood and in his mid to late
OL,16,Fteens was told by his mother that
OL,17,FDavid Rich was his father.
