OL,3,CMan who stalked Strictly star for
OL,4,Cyears avoids being sent to jail
OL,6,FHe said: "He now accepts that Miss
OL,7,FBallas and her family don't wish to
OL,8,Fhave any contact with him and,
OL,9,Fimportantly, he volunteered the
OL,10,Finformation that he has no intention
OL,11,Fof contacting them again."
OL,13,FShaw, wearing a white shirt and tie
OL,14,Fwith a black coat, wiped away tears at
OL,15,Ftimes during the hearing and sobbed in
OL,16,Fthe dock when Judge Gary Woodhall
OL,17,Fdelivered the sentence. He was made
OL,18,Fthe subject of a restraining order for
OL,19,Flife which prevented him contacting
OL,20,FBallas as well as her niece, mother
OL,21,Fand former partner.
